Name: Delicious Solitaire
About the game: Delicous Solitaire cleverly combines themes like palate-pleasing and kitchen dreams with a popular card game. Unlock many solitaire levels with very appetizing looking backgrounds and enjoy different solitaire variations with a matching set of cards. The program is suitable for beginners as well as for the experienced solitaire player and offers challenging gameplay! - Solitaire game with many challenging levels - Beautiful backgrounds with matching card set - Various locations on the theme of palate pleasers - Suitable for beginners and solitaire pros alike
